+``/var/log/syslog``).
+
+RFC-3164 omits the year. We use a reference date (default: today) and infer the
+year: if the parsed month is *after* the reference month we assume the entry is
+from the previous year. This handles the common case of analyzing December
+entries in January/February/etc.
